{"tid":475552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"追薪15.8萬元 李偲嫣被判敗訴","createTime":"2017-11-21T08:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T01:44:15.000Z","uid":39464,"like":85,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"741a6097c9cd8575ac49cfc87c0d5935f1b56c65","tid":475552,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:23:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171121/large/1511241662_02b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171121%2Flarge%2F1511241662_02b8.jpg&h=d9b8b491&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正義聯盟創黨主席李偲嫣，聲稱遭網媒欠薪及墊支費，於勞資審裁處向對方索共約15.8萬元。惟審裁官今指李未能證明與兩被告有僱傭關係，裁定李敗訴，並須賠償逾600元訟費。<br />\n<br />\n兩被告網購無限有限公司（前稱匯傳媒）及營運網台HKBC.TV的媒體無限有限公司，被申索人李偲嫣追討2015年12月的半個月欠薪、代通知金、有薪年假、墊支雜費等共約15.8萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171121/57484989\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171121%2F57484989&d=mg95djlf9FHQSCc7LfRtzzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=48ad79c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171121%2F57484989&h=dff50e5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171121/57484989</a>"},{"pid":"ebfce5c22f0418875b49f69493d9dbd888c69b7e","tid":475552,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:25:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"245b625bc7deb68909d9cbcf973d2a1d5f1393de","tid":475552,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:25:30.000Z","msg":"600元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0087d0556699b201dc7a4ec2cfaf93486beb95ec","tid":475552,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:26:02.000Z","m